Description:
Pure Opulence Off-The-Plan
Please visit our showroom at 989 Doncaster Road, Doncaster East at open times or by appointment.
Available to purchase off-the-plan, this boutique collection of only two tri-level homes ensures a lifestyle of ease and privacy. With identical floorplans, each dwelling has been cleverly designed to feature spacious living domains, accommodating bedrooms, and a large backyard. Perfect for a family, they contain high quality fittings and fixtures including square set cornices and engineered timber floors.
The entry levels are the hub of activity; they feature a large family/meals area, study and master bedroom (with ensuite & BIR) as well as a stunning alfresco setting. The spectacular entertainer’s kitchens have butler’s pantries and are equipped with Miele appliances, Paco Jaanson sinks and tapware, stone benches, mirrored splashbacks and two-pac cabinetry.
Upstairs, each bedroom offers ample wardrobe space. Bedrooms 2 and 3 share a twin vanity bathroom while bedroom 4 boasts its own ensuite. A convenient guest bedroom is located on the lower level alongside a rumpus, study/library and deck.
Additional first-class conveniences to these state-of-the-art homes include remote double garages, exposed aggregate driveways, intercom, ducted heating and cooling. The location adds further value, only a short distance from Westfield, the Eastern Freeway, Doncaster Primary and Secondary schools, and bus services.
Insights: 29 other 5 bedroom house in Doncaster have recently been sold.

Description:
Executive style and sophistication.
A stunning example of glamorous, contemporary architecture, you will be challenged to find a single instance of quality compromised within this superbly crafted executive residence, which boasts its own stylish frontage, its own title with no common land and a first-class setting in a sought-after Doncaster pocket.
A captivating façade showcasing contrasting textures and finishes draws you into this celebration of modern living that features premium-grade fixtures and fittings, meticulous attention to detail, loads of natural light and a fantastic mix of two separate living zones plus four bedrooms of generous proportions.
Beneath the square-set high ceilings of the radiant ground-floor layout flow beautiful polished timber floors, which accompany your every step past the carpeted formal lounge/dining of an elegant character en route to a spectacular open-plan setting. With enough room to fit a large dining table, a vibrant living area that spills out onto a stunning North-facing alfresco and sleek kitchen styled with stone benchtops, easy-to-clean splashback, generous storage and quality stainless steel appliances, it's a fitting centrepiece to such a lavish home.
Three generously sized bedrooms (Master with ensuite and private balcony offering sweeping views) enjoy the privacy of the upstairs floorplan along with an excellent main bathroom, while a fourth bedroom downstairs is serviced by a powder room to present peaceful accommodation for overnight guests or extended family members.
Protected by an alarm system with the added benefit of video intercom and complete with a gas ducted heating, evaporative cooling, ducted vacuum and a remote double garage, this is a home to be enjoyed.
Completing the appeal of this flawless property is its coveted location, which enjoys brilliant access to the CBD via the Eastern Freeway, the popular Koonung Creek Trail, bus services, Westfield Shoppingtown, trendy eateries, nearby schools and Ruffey Lake Park.

The striking, high-end kitchen is equipped with Miele appliances, stone benches and an under-mounted sink. Description:
Great Block With DD08 Overlay
741sqm approx. of prime Doncaster land, in a General Residential Zone with a DD08 overlay, is sure to attract a significant amount of attention.
Builders and developers, could this be the site for your next exciting project (STCA)? Think about the scope you'd have. The bonus here is that this quality allotment also comes with a substantial home; boasting 5 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and dual living zones, it offers the potential to enjoy rental income whilst you are planning your endeavour.
The area is highly sought and amenity rich; you're within close proximity to Westfield Doncaster for both shopping and entertainment, local buses, Eastlink/Eastern freeway, popular schools including Doncaster Secondary College to which you are zoned, plus a number of parks, reserves and open green spaces.
Opportunities of this nature are highly sought but rarely found, so be quick to ensure you're not left living with regret.

Description:
High-end executive living with multi-generational living options.
Crafted to exacting standards with a remarkably versatile two-storey floorplan, this refined town residence has the rare ability to function seamlessly as an executive abode for the power couple or spacious home for those with multi-generational living requirements.
Its soaring clinker brick façade projects an image of sophistication that extends to the pristine interior, dressed with high quality appointments, rich timber floorboards, abundant natural light, wonderful high ceilings and textured feature walls that accentuate the home's cultured character. A statement of high-end living with a low maintenance edge, it's also a home that deceives with its grand sense of space achieved with three separate living zones and four bedrooms of a generous nature.
A vast downstairs bedroom with separate living and sleeping area, full ensuite, large built-in robes and own entry is a rare feature you're unlikely to find in many other properties on the market. Perfect for extended family members or an older child, the bedroom can also be converted into a consulting suite for professionals running a business from home.
The elegant formal lounge and dining rooms are arranged around a captivating central atrium, which draws maximum sunlight into the home, while seamless indoor-outdoor living is a design feature embraced by the sun-kissed open-plan living, which interacts visually and physically with the private courtyard and features a recently renovated kitchen equipped with stone benchtops, 900mm stainless steel cooker and excellent storage options.
The home's impressive size and scale extends to the oversized Master bedroom, which connects with two balconies and is serviced by a fully-tiled ensuite with a double shower. Two additional bedrooms also benefit from their private zoning upstairs and easy access to a central toilet and fully-tiled bathroom with a spa bath.
Complete with a carpeted rumpus downstairs, large laundry, ducted heating, three split-system units, loads of storage, Rinnai Infinity hot water system, generous off-street parking and concreted storage area under the house plus convenient access to the Park + Ride, the Eastern Freeway, numerous schooling options, Village Ave and Macedon Square shops, Westfield Shoppingtown, parks and bus services (both within walking distance), this standout residence is made for the buyer who demands absolute perfection.

Description:
Perfect for now, perfect for the future
Elevated on the high side of the street with sweeping rear views to Westfield Shoppingtown, this delightful 1960's home offers current comforts plus tempting scope to redevelop on 794sqm in the heart of Doncaster. Easy to live in or easy to rent out, the attractive 3 bedroom floorplan is flooded with sunlight and lined in hardwood timber floors throughout large lounge, neat modern kitchen and meals area with treetop valley views. Description:
Stunning luxurious 3 bedroom apartment with CBD skyline views
This luxurious, modern three bedroom (or two bedroom plus study) apartment holds stunning skyline views of Melbourne CBD, and with its Doncaster Hill location is convenient with easy access to everything.
Quality fittings immediately capture your attention, with rich, solid timber floors extend throughout, and custom black cube downlight fixtures adding a distinctive touch to the space. Modern designed kitchen, with engineered stone benches, marble splash-back, plus Miele appliances attached to the island counter, which extends to the living and dining area further opening out to a large balcony.
There are three rooms which are generously sized, with the third room granting a great opportunity for use as either a bedroom, study, or leisure. The master bedroom, with built-in robes, quality en-suite and a private balcony. Other fittings including reverse cycle heating and cooling, a separate euro inspired laundry, and a spacious family bathroom.
The apartment also offers a rooftop garden and gym, elevator, security intercom, 2 underground parking, and storage. And city is just a short drive away and easy access to freeway and public transport. World-class shopping centre - Westfield Doncaster is right on your doorstep, with quality schools and leisure parks all nearby.

Professional couples, the young family and downsizing buyers still requiring space for the grandkids will be overjoyed with this low maintenance four-bedroom Townhouse of distinction, matched by a sought-after Doncaster address loaded with lifestyle advantages.

The home itself is superbly presented and the family will be spoilt with two large bedrooms plus third which can be used as a study. Light and bright kitchen and meals area, separate laundry and well-appointed original bathroom.
The beautiful tranquil gardens all-culminating to produce a picturesque outdoor living setting and ideal for every occasion.
Features include: ducted heating, split system cooling in the bedroom, air-conditioning in the kitchen/ meals area, polished timber flooring throughout.
Large tandem carport, garage and store room/work shop plus much more!!

Description:
The Ultimate in Urban Living
Located in the heart of Doncaster with cafés, restaurants and entertainment at your fingertips, this brand new three bedroom apartment promotes a luxurious yet low maintenance lifestyle. Immersed in natural light, the interior boasts an open-plan living domain with study nook overseen by a sleek kitchen fitted with Miele appliances and stone benches. An idyllic spot for alfresco entertaining, the wrap-around balcony is an impressive feature. Each of spacious proportions, the bedrooms are handily equipped with built-in robes and serviced by a modern bathroom, the master also with an ensuite. Just moments from the attractions of Westfield Doncaster, this stunning home is also close to Park+Ride and bus services.
Additional Features:
*Rare to find parking for 2 vehicles
*Intercom system & heating/AC unit
*Concealed European-style laundry
*Floor-to-ceiling tiles in bathrooms
*Near parks incl. Schramm’s Reserve
*Easy access to the Eastern Freeway

Description:
Convenient Living in a Fantastic Location!
Be amazed with the style and sophistication this huge 114sqm (approx.) apartment brings with natural light radiating through the floor to ceiling windows placed throughout the home with a fantastic view of the Dandenong Mountains!
With stunning parquetry floors placed in the open plan living and dining room which opens up to a balcony, offering a place for alfresco dining to entertain guests. A well-equipped modern kitchen completes the space boasting stone benchtops, stainless steel appliances and ample storage.
Three generous bedrooms are zoned together; each has built-in robes and the master has its own private ensuite. The remaining two are serviced by a central bathroom; both offer large vanities with good storage, square basins and oversized showers.
There are a multitude of extras that complete this stylish apartment; high ceilings, deep skirting boards, panelled doors, quality carpets, intercom system, 2 split systems plus a separate laundry.
The building has a secure entrance foyer and lift access to all floors including the basement where you have two carparks and a lockable storage cage.
You will love the perks of residing at this address being within walking distance to local buses and Westfield Doncaster, easy Freeway access and only a short drive to the delights of central Box Hill. Also situated in the Doncaster Primary and Doncaster Secondary College zone, sending your children to school will be a delight.
Call today to arrange an inspection on 9840 7700.

Superb space, scope and serenity
Pleasantly situated on 768sqm approx, surrounded by beautiful gardens with magnificent treetop vistas and upper floor city views, this smartly proportioned 4 bedroom (with scope for a fifth bedroom if required), 2 bathroom home delivers broad family appeal and grand future potential to all buyers. Privately zoned upstairs are the bedrooms and bathroom, master with WIR and ensuite. Features include ducted heating, A/C, downstairs powder room, laundry and D/G. Inviting endless options to all buyers, move in and enjoy, update and renovate or build a luxurious new home or townhouses STCA. The premium location minutes to freeway, Park and Ride, Macedon Square and Westfield shopping surrounded by excellent schools and zoned to Doncaster Secondary College, the lifestyle advantages are sensational.
